<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
    <!--
      App Groups + Siri/CarPlay entitlements are intentionally omitted for now.

      • App Groups (group.com.lightwave.zeus) can only be provisioned with an
        Apple-ID login, not an App Store Connect API key, so it can't be signed
        on CI without one-time portal setup. Re-add once the group is created in
        the developer portal and enabled on both App IDs. (Needed for the widget
        to share live vehicle data with the app.)
      • App Intents (the Siri feature) do NOT require the com.apple.developer.siri
        entitlement, so it's removed.
      • CarPlay requires an Apple-granted entitlement (request separately).
    -->
</dict>
</plist>
